      <title>加拿大 Eight Capital 即将关闭，Stifel 将收购银行家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/canada-s-eight-capital-to-shut-down-as-stifel-swoops-in-for-bankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加拿大投资交易商 Eight Capital Corp. 即将倒闭，其许多高层员工将转投 Stifel Financial Corp.。]]></description>
