      <title>美国核心通胀降温后亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四亚洲股市跟随华尔街上涨，因美国核心通胀率下降，美联储今年降息的前景仍未改变。日元因日本央行加息预期而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 22:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
